{
  "stem": "18102.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only through memory can we prevent making-- the world making the same mistake again and again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And obviously, I wanted, also, to preserve the name of Sugihara in the process of memorializing the events of the Holocaust, to prevent their reoccurrence.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I believe that it is through education of this sort, both in visual form at the museum, as well as in written and academic form otherwise, that we can prevent such a reoccurrence.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Unfortunately, it continues to plague humankind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There are always those who would commit genocide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Rwanda comes to mind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And although it isn't on the same magnitude as was the Holocaust the Jews suffered, but nevertheless, it has the genocidal incidents that make it similar.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And unfortunately, these things and events will, again, happen if we are not always on guard against the seeds of hatred being allowed to grow anywhere in the world, to any people of the world.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wish I could tell you that there will be more incidences of that than there have been.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We know that during the-- during the war-- during the Holocaust, there were precious few that stepped out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Raoul Wallenberg, of course, is well-remembered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Schindler is well-remembered, and Sugihara.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there is a handful of those against the millions that did nothing and, in fact, had a deaf ear and a blind eye to all that occurred.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, that is what bothered me, as an adult, more than anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where were the religious leaders of the world?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where were the philosophers, academicians?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where were the government officials?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where were the average people who should have protested and not allowed?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and their voice alone should have torn down the walls of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
